gobblin.runtime.job_catalog

Class PackagedTemplatesJobCatalogDecorator

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.runtime.job_catalog.PackagedTemplatesJobCatalogDecorator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Instrumentable, JobCatalog, JobCatalogListenersContainer, JobCatalogWithTemplates, Decorator

    public class PackagedTemplatesJobCatalogDecorator
extends Object
implements Decorator, JobCatalogWithTemplates
    A Decorator for JobCatalog that loads JobTemplates from classpath (resources and classes). This decorator will intercept JobTemplate requests with schemes "resource" or "class", and will load them from classpath. * A class template has uri "class://fully.qualified.class.name", and will instantiate that class and attempt to cast as JobTemplate. * A resource template has uri "resource:///path/to/template/in/resources.template", and the decorator will attempt to parse it as a ResourceBasedJobTemplate. * Any other scheme will be delegated to the underlying job catalog if it implements JobCatalogWithTemplates, or a SpecNotFoundException will be thrown.
